AWS EventBridge rule triggering a Lambda function on new weather data:

{
  "Source": ["aws.weather"],
  "DetailType": ["WeatherUpdate"],
  "Detail": {"eventType": ["Rain"]}
}

Airflow DAG for multi-source ingestion:

def ingest_sources():
    nasa = fetch_nasa()
    noaa = fetch_noaa()
    radar = fetch_radar()
    return merge([nasa, noaa, radar])
